%h2 About Teiid
.well
  Teiid offers a relational abstraction of all information sources that is highly performant and allows for integration with your existing relational tools. Teiid has an accompanying easy-to-use
  %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/tools"} design tool
  that enables data architects to integrate disparate information in minutes.&nbsp;
%p
  Teiid has a
  = succeed "of" do
    %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/about/history"} long history
  addressing the data access needs of any size enterprise environment.&nbsp; Have a look at
  = succeed "," do
    %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/about/why"} Why Teiid?
  our
  = succeed "," do
    %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/about/featurematrix"} feature matrix
  and
  %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/about/faq"} FAQ
  to see if this project is a good fit for your needs.
%p
  Best of all, Teiid is
  %a{:href => "#{site.base_url}/about/license"} open source
  and a part of the
  %a{:href => "http://jboss.org"} JBoss Community
  of projects.
.clear
